---
Syntax: visible

Removes all invisibility, concealment, and stealth effects from your
character, making you fully visible to everyone in the room. This is useful
when you want to be seen after sneaking, hiding, or using invisibility spells.

Effects removed by VISIBLE:
  - Sneak (AFF_SNEAK)
  - Invisibility (AFF_INVISIBLE)
  - Mass Invisibility (AFF_MASS_INVIS)
  - Hide status

Message: "You become more visible again."

Note: Some effects may be reapplied by spells or skills -- for example,
if a permanent-duration invisibility spell is active, you may need to
dispel it specifically or allow it to wear off naturally.

See also: hide sneak shadowform invis cast dispel magic
